{
  "stem": "13213.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I said, no, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'll go back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In the meantime, I, I got some vacation, more vacation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I wrote to El Al that I would like to stay here longer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was-- I met a guy by the name of [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Norman ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Lachance ?] who was in the American Air Force.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we started to talk, and he said they need mechanics in the Air Force.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I went and applied, and I got a job in the Air Force in the town of Erding.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was a big airbase in Bavaria in Erding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I worked-- I lived in a youth hostel and worked for the American Air Force as a mechanic.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They send me on a course to finish hydraulic mechanic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I worked as a hydraulic mechanic on landing gears for the new jets, which were the F-86 at the time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And since I worked there, I just decided to stay for a little while.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was-- let's face it, in Israel times were very tough.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Here the food was good, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And my cousin was assisting-- Shabtai Waks was his name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That's my uncle's son from Stepan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He's the whole time trying to talk me into to stay and go to the States.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was still-- he didn't leave yet until for while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then the Korean War broke out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow, I felt that they had enough of wars, and I didn't want to go to the States or anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My friend Norman Lachance, who was Canadian, said, well, if you're not going to the States, why don't you come to Canada?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know much about Canada except when I was in Israel, and I was fantasizing about some countries, sometimes where there's gold.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
